	<region id="editorData">
		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="Load Act 3. Teleport to the circus. Shadow and Crimson are currently by Dribbles and in seperate cages. Feed Crimson and trap Shadow before triggering the fight in order for them to survive and have subsequent dialogues after the fight." />
			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="279" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="Crimson the dinosaur is one of the animals who will participate in the doppelganger-dribbles attack. Player can examine him and realise Crimson isn't angry, he's starving. If the player feeds him some meat, he is so busy eating during the attack that he doesn't participate.&#xD;&#xA;In the bottom branch, he's so hungry that he's on the brink of losing his mind - he's snapping, furious, and all he craves is meat." />
			<children>
				<node id="defaultAttitudes">
					<children>
						<node id="data">
